              <p>引き算の先にたどり着いた<br class="SP">Simple is the ultimate luxury.</p>
              <br class="SPnone">
              <br class="SPnone">
              <div class="btnBox">
                  <a href="https://srolanie.myshopify.com/pages/chapter">
                      <button>View Collection</button>      
                  </a>   
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
